<DATELINE>OAKLAND, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   One-time Black Panther Eldridge Cleaver
was placed on three years' probation for a misdemeanor burglary
conviction.
   Oakland Municipal Court Judge Horace Wheatley on Monday also
gave Cleaver a suspended 180-day jail term, ordered him to perform
200 hours of volunteer work and told him to make restitution.
   Cleaver pleaded no contest to a misdemeanor burglary charge in a
